data.text: Look Ahead Toward the Ultimate Goal!
data.notes: When you first set your goals, where did you want to be at the end of 2024? With the pace you're setting at nearly halfway through, is your goal still realistic? If not, think about adjusting your goal to better fit your pace.
Towards the end of the month reflect on your progress so far and your hopes for the coming months. It may be helpful to make notes about how you're doing or share with an accountability buddy.
